---

<Layout title={HOME.TITLE} description={HOME.DESCRIPTION}>
  <section>
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Hello!</h3>
    <article class="space-y-4">
      <span class="animate">
        <p>
          I'm Antonio Valentini, a software engineer with over 12 years of
          experience, passionate about solving real-world problems with
          technology. My expertise lies in building data-intensive backend
          systems and mobile applications, with a strong focus on <code
            >.NET/C#</code
          > and scalable system architectures.
        </p>
        <p>
          From time to time I also like to post some videos on my ðŸ“º YouTube
          channel, where I share insights and tutorials about cross-platform
          tools and applications, such as AvaloniaUI.
        </p>
        <p>
          Beyond coding, youll often find me snowboarding, experimenting with
          electronics, or sipping on great coffee. Check out <a href="/blog"
            >my blog</a
          > for insights on software engineering, tutorials, and tech experiments.
        </p>
      </span>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="animate space-y-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-y-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
              Latest posts
            </h2>
            <ul class="not-prose flex flex-col gap-4">
            {
              blog.map((post) => (
                <li>
                  {/* <ArrowCard entry={post} /> */}
                  <a href={`/${post.collection}/${post.id}`}>{post.data.title}</a>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
            <a href="/blog"> See all posts </a>
          </div>
          
        </section>
</Layout>
